---
---

<section id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-col">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <h2>Prenons <em>rendez-vous</em></h2>
      <p>
        Vous souhaitez en savoir plus ou réserver une séance ?
        N'hésitez pas à me contacter, je vous répondrai avec plaisir.
      </p>

      <div class="info-list">
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.79 19.79 0 0 1 2.12 4.18 2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="label">Téléphone</p>
            <a href="tel:+33633738764">06 33 73 87 64</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="label">Localisation</p>
            <p>Fayence, Var (83)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="deco-col">
      <div class="deco-card">
        <div class="quote">
          &laquo;&nbsp;Le soin commence par une présence sincère et une écoute profonde.&nbsp;&raquo;
        </div>
        <img src="/rdv.jpg" alt="Prise de contact" class="contact-img" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    background: var(--color-beige);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5rem;
  }

  .text-col {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .deco-col {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--color-green-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-green);
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .info-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-green-pale);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .info-icon svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    color: var(--color-green);
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .info-item a {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-green-dark);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .info-item a:hover {
    color: var(--color-green);
  }

  .info-item > div > p:last-child {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-green-dark);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
  }

  .deco-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(74, 103, 65, 0.08);
  }

  .quote {
    padding: 2rem 2rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-green-dark);
    line-height: 1.6;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-gold);
    margin: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .contact-img {
    display: block;
    width: calc(100% - 3rem);
    margin: 1.5rem;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .deco-col {
      max-width: 100%;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
